### Section 5 — Significance Filtering
```{r fdr}
# Option A: BH-corrected FDR (uncomment for multiple testing correction)
# bos      <- read.csv(outputPath, header = TRUE)
# bos$pAdj <- p.adjust(bos$obsP, method = "BH")
# bos      <- bos[bos$pAdj < pThreshold, ]

# Option B: Nominal p (exploratory)
bos <- read.csv(outputPath, header = TRUE)
bos <- bos[bos$obsP < pThreshold, ]

cat("Significant associations:", nrow(bos), "\n")
```

